data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bath home spanning 3024 square feet. With plantation shutters throughout, it's move-in ready for you. Recent upgrades include a new roof in 2022, HVAC units in 2017 with new high efficiency, multi speed air handlers, dual-pane, low-E windows (with transferable  warranty for breakage and defect) in 2017, CPVC pipe removed and replaced with PEX plumbing in 2021- not due to leaks, just proactively caring well for their home, pool pump in 2020, and a filter in 2018. The master bedroom features dual walk-in closets and a spacious sitting area. The master bath offers a garden tub, shower, and double sinks. Timeless finishes adorn the remodeled 2nd and 3rd baths. Situated on a large lot, the outdoor space includes a grassy area, play pool, gazebo, and BBQ. the view fencing backing up to a green belt. Additional features include a 3-car garage pre-plumbed for a sink, water filtration, and a generous laundry room with cabinets above washer and dryer. A downstairs bedroom has access to a bathroom with a walk-in shower. Inside, discover soaring vaulted ceilings, a grand staircase, timeless neutral tile, and upgraded carpet. The extra-large formal living and dining area set the stage for elegant gatherings. The open-concept kitchen, complete with a walk-in pantry, stainless appliances, and abundant cabinets, seamlessly connects with the family room highlighted by a beautiful gas fireplace. This home offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionalitytruly a haven for modern living.
